{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "本章介绍主角孟星魂——一个以杀人为生的孤独剑客。他受高大姐（高寄萍）指派，任务是在四个月内刺杀江南大豪孙王伫。孟星魂回忆了自己六岁时被高大姐收养的经历，以及第一次刺杀金枪李的经过。他来到快活林，与一个持紫金鱼鳞刀的狂徒发生冲突，将其打成重伤。高大姐前来催促任务，孟星魂表达了对杀人的厌倦，但在高大姐的劝说下勉强答应。高大姐试图以身体诱惑他，孟星魂却无法接受她既是姐姐又是母亲的角色，仓皇逃离。他在快活林观察来客，试图寻找买主的身份线索，暗中开始了对孙王伫的调查行动。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_nv_zi_a",
      "speaker_name": "女子甲",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你溜到那里去了，害得我们连酒都喝不下去了。",
      "tone": "娇嘟",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "滚！",
      "tone": "冰冷",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_jin_dao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "紫金刀客",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你叫她们滚？",
      "tone": "质问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_zi_jin_dao_ke",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "冰淡",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_jin_dao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "紫金刀客",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你醉了，连我是谁都忘了。我是你从三花楼请来的客人，我们本来是在那里喝酒碰上的，你一定要请我来。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_jin_dao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "紫金刀客",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我来，是因为你这里有女人，你怎么能叫她们滚？",
      "tone": "沉脸",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_zi_jin_dao_ke",
      "text": "你也滚！",
      "tone": "冰冷",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_jin_dao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "紫金刀客",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_zi_jin_dao_ke",
      "text": "滚！",
      "tone": "冰冷",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_jin_dao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "紫金刀客",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你就算醉糊涂了，就算是忘了我是谁，也不该忘了这把紫金鱼鳞刀！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_zi_jin_dao_ke",
      "text": "你用这柄刀杀过人？",
      "tone": "冷峻",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_jin_dao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "紫金刀客",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "当然！",
      "tone": "傲慢",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_zi_jin_dao_ke",
      "text": "杀过多少人？",
      "tone": "冰淡",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_jin_dao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "紫金刀客",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "二十个，也许还不止，谁记得这种事。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_jin_dao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "紫金刀客",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "今天我却不想杀人，何况我又喝了你的酒，用过你的女人……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mou_ren",
      "speaker_name": "某人",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "这次我坐庄，老板娘要不要过来押一注？",
      "tone": "吐哀",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高大姐",
      "listener": "char_song_san",
      "text": "这是闹着玩的，算不得认真，宋三爷身上若是不方便就学两声狗叫，让大家乐一乐，这次赌的就算是狗叫。",
      "tone": "戏谎",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高大姐",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你不该喝酒的。",
      "tone": "温柔而带命令",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "你是来催我的？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高大姐",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你从来用不着我催，也从来没有让我失望。",
      "tone": "温和",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "但这次……",
      "tone": "犹警",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高大姐",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "这次怎么样？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "这次我不去行不行？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高大姐",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "为什么？你怕孙王伫？",
      "tone": "猛然严厉",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "我只是不想去。",
      "tone": "疲倦",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高大姐",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "不行，你非去不可。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高大姐",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你知道，石群在西北，小何人了京，暂时都回不来。何况，这件事只有你能做，只有你才能对付孙王伫。",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "号翔呢？",
      "tone": "试探",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高大姐",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "号翔？他现在只能抱抱孩子。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "他以前做过的。",
      "tone": "辩护",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高大姐",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "以前是以前。",
      "tone": "冰淡",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高大姐",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我已经给过他三次机会，我不能再让付令我失望一次。",
      "tone": "柔和",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高大姐",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "不要跟我争了，我已经累得很……",
      "tone": "疲倦",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高大姐",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我知道你也累得很，但生活就是这样子的，我们要活下去，就不能停下来。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "你若一定要我去，我就去。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高大姐",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我知道你绝不会令我失望。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高大姐",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你已经不是个孩子了。",
      "tone": "轻叹",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高大姐",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我知道你找过很多女人呢！",
      "tone": "暗春",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "很多。",
      "tone": "简短",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高大姐",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你有没有喜欢过她们？",
      "tone": "探究",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "简短",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高大姐",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你若不喜欢她们，她们就无法令你满足，一个人若永远不能满足就会觉得厌倦。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高大姐",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "也许，你根本还不懂得女人，还不知道一个女人能给男人多么大的鼓舞。",
      "tone": "婩媚",
      "chapter": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高大姐",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你若懂得女人，就不会再厌倦，我要教你懂得……",
      "tone": "温柔而遥远",
      "chapter": 1
    }
  ],
